  <p>After two players have completed a challenge, neither player can challenge each other again until next week. Each player can continue to challenge other players though for ladder positions during the same meeting. 
  <p>If players ranked above you on the ladder are not at the current meeting, you can skip their positions when choosing someone to challenge. For example:
